  <brief_title>A Trial on Conservative Treatment for Infants' Hirschsprung Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Randomized Controlled Trial of Conservative Versus Surgery Treatment of Normal and Short-segment Hirschsprung Disease for Infants</official_title>
  <sponsors>
